  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to find out if motexafin gadolinium may be an effective
      treatment for patients with non-Hodgkin's lymphoma (NHL). Secondly, the safety and side
      effects of motexafin gadolinium will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
